snippet.title: ANOTHER Reason Why A Border Fence Is A Stupid Idea

localized.description:
A new study has confirmed that building a multi-billion dollar border fence is a stupid idea. It could actually lead to more permanent undocumented immigrants. John Iadarola, host of ThinkTank, delivers his Final Judgment on border security backfiring.

Do you think we should build a wall? Let us know in the comments below.

Hosts: John Iadarola

Cast: John Iadarola
